&lt;li&gt;Other general tasks include endorsement processing &amp;amp; billing, reviewing notice of cancellations, analysis of loss data within Experience Mods, deductible analysis and participation in internal review meetings and other meetings as requested.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently, lead project special assignments.&lt;/li&gt;
