&lt;li&gt;Applicable experience required with specialty experience preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail &amp;amp; ability to work within AMS and maintain data completeness standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Achieved general insurance designation. Pursuing other insurance designation - preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project / time management skills to manage multiple priorities and to keep processes moving from start to finish&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with MS Office products required (specifically PowerPoint, Outlook, Word, Excel)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Limited travel required (less than 10%)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competencies &amp;amp; Traits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
